content_raw: Congratulations! You have just learned the basics of Docusaurus and made some changes to the initial template. Docusaurus has much more to offer! Have 5 more minutes? Take a look at versioning and i18n. Anything unclear or buggy in this tutorial? Please report it! What's next? - Read the official documentation - Modify your site configuration with docusaurus.config.js - Add navbar and footer items with themeConfig - Add a custom Design and Layout - Add a search bar - Find inspirations in the Docusaurus showcase - Get involved in the Docusaurus Community
